description: Gets the License Manager settings for the current Region.

nested_items.name: S3BucketArn
nested_items.description: Regional S3 bucket path for storing reports, license trail event data, discovery data, and so on.

nested_items.name: SnsTopicArn
nested_items.description: SNS topic configured to receive notifications from License Manager.

nested_items.name: OrganizationConfiguration
nested_items.description: Indicates whether Organizations is integrated with License Manager for cross-account discovery.

nested_items.name: EnableCrossAccountsDiscovery
nested_items.description: Indicates whether cross-account discovery is enabled.

nested_items.name: LicenseManagerResourceShareArn
nested_items.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource share. The License Manager management account provides member accounts with access to this share.
